title: [The Cobbler's Cobby, Registrar]
description: A collection of strange and exotic creatures in magnificent detail crowd the surface of a polished oak table.  Sunlight produces a spectrum of colors as it filters through several of the hand-blown glass figurines that are perched on the table directly beneath the window.  Apparently used for storing, the overflow of stacks of paper and ledgers rest atop of a lacquered bench.
